[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]EDF Energy is one of the 
[normal]UK
[normal]’s largest energy companies with activities throughout the energy chain. We provide 50% of the 
[normal]UK
[normal]’s low carbon generation. Our interests include nuclear, coal and gas-fired electricity generation, renewables, and energy supply to end users. We have over five million electricity and gas customer accounts in the 
[normal]UK
[normal], including both residential and business users.
